OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and clear. Then the rest
OL,7,Fof the night will be dry with lengthy
OL,8,Fclear spells. A cold night with a
OL,9,Ffrost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,12,Fbright spells across the north. More
OL,13,Fin the way of cloud across the south.
OL,14,FThe odd shower later. A mild day
OL,15,Facross northern Moray.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,18,Fspreading east on Thursday afternoon,
OL,19,Fclearing early on Friday. Then Friday
OL,20,Fand Saturday will be dry with some
OL,21,Fbrightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
